<h5><%= Date.today.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %></h5>
<p>
Greetings,
</p>

<p>Thank you for shopping with Unbelievable Books: Literature that's Out of this Nebula! Your order has been placed and you can expect your books in less than 12 parsecs.</p>

<div class="order">
  <h3>Your Order:</h3>
  <ul>
    <% @order.order_items.each do |item| %>
      <li class="order-item">
        <%= item.quantity %>
        <em><%= item.product.name %></em>
        $<%= item.reserved_price %> each |
        $<%= item.reserved_price * item.quantity %> total
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Order total: $<%= @order.price_total %></strong></p>
  <p><strong>With Tax: $<%= @order.get_final_price %></strong></p>
</div>

<p>Thank you for your patronage!</p>

<p>~Unbelievable Booksellers</p>
